          "x1": 24,
          "y1": 194,
          "x2": 366,
          "y2": 194,
          "stroke": "#1E2438",
          "strokeWidth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "An AI agent pursues a goal by iteratively taking",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 212,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#E9EDF6",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "actions, evaluating progress, and deciding next steps.",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 232,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#E9EDF6",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Unlike a single-shot LLM call, the agent runs a loop:",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 272,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#E9EDF6",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "  1.  Observe — capture the current world state",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 312,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#58697F",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "  2.  Reason — choose the best next action",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 332,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#58697F",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "  3.  Act — execute a tool or generate output",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 352,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#58697F",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "  4.  Evaluate — measure how close to the goal",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 372,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#34D399",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "The eval step is the hardest. Without it, agents",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 412,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#E9EDF6",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "hallucinate completion rather than measure it.",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 432,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#E9EDF6",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "See → Agentic UX must surface loop state to users.",
          "x": 24,
          "y": 472,
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "regular",
          "color": "#7C6EF2",
          "align": "left",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
